songs.title: Sweet Sue - Just You
songs.lyrics:
Every star above
Knows the one I love
Sweet Sue, sweet Sue

And the moon up high
Knows the reason why
Sweet Sue - just you!

No one else it seems
Ever shared my dreams
And without you, dear, I don't know what I'd do

In this heart of mine
You live all the time
Sweet Sue, sweet Sue

(Instrumental)

(Vocals)

Every star above
Knows the one I love
Sweet Sue, sweet Sue

And the moon up high
Knows the reason why
Sweet Sue - just you!

No one else it seems
Ever shared my dreams
And without you, dear, I don't know what I'd do

In this heart of mine
You live all the time
Sweet Sue, sweet Sue
Sweet Sue
